WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Hi! Welcome to the Reentry Assistant.

2
00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:15.000
To ensure you're set up for success, here are a few grounding instructions.

3
00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:21.000
This helps them understand the best way to support you as you transition back into the community.

4
00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:27.000
As you answer the following questions, you will be interacting with a chatbot, not a live person.

5
00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:41.000
The questions will cover topics related to education, employment, finances, health, family, housing, hobbies, and alcohol and drugs. Be as open as you are comfortable being!

6
00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:45.000
Your response to this intake will be visible only to IDOC staff.

8
00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:52.000
A few important notes:

9
00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:58.000
Some questions might require careful thought. Feel free to pause and reflect as much as you need.

10
00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:05.000
Your progress is automatically saved, so you can leave the intake chat and return later if you need to pause.

11
00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:12.000
This intake should be completed before your next meeting with your case manager. The sooner you can finish it, the better.

12
00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:19.000
Now, let's get ready. Press "Start Intake" to begin.
